  "title": "Senior Executive, Academic & Residential Experience | Boon Lay / Pioneer MRT",
  "description": "<p>A member of the Academic & Residential Experience unit, Senior Executive (ARE) will support ARE in administrative tasks necessary to achieve Student Affairs Office (SAO) objectives through a portfolio of academic, scholar related clubs and hall councils.</p><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Student Community Engagement (ARE) programme/project administration including project applications, claim submissions/reimbursements and reporting.</li><li>Manage clubs and hall council purchases and asset procurement & management</li><li>Maintenance of Student Community Engagement databases and the preparation of management and other reporting requirements.</li><li>Support the development and communication of ARE publicity materials and maintenance of its publicity portals</li><li>Manage facilities booking requests</li><li>Support other ARE administrative requirements as assigned e.g., meeting arrangements, meeting minutes, support at SAO events etc</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in any discipline. Fresh grads are welcomed to apply.</li><li>Candidates with 1-2 years of experience in supporting programme/project administration including processing of programme budgets, funding  claims/reimbursements and reporting requirements would have an added advantage</li><li>Proficient in all Microsoft applications especially Excel and Power Automate.</li><li>Highly organised and meticulous.</li><li>Able to forward planning, anticipate needs, with a strong initiative to take ownership of tasks assigned and make appropriate recommendations.</li><li>Ability to effectively manage multi-task concurrently and adapt to changes well.</li><li>Good team player with excellent interpersonal skills </li></ul><p><br /><strong>Working Arrangement</strong></p><ul><li>Monday to Thursday: 8.30am – 5.45pm</li><li>Friday: 8.30am – 5.15pm</li><li>Sat/Sun: Off</li></ul><p><strong>Contract Duration</strong>: 1 year<br /><strong>Location</strong>: Boon Lay / Pioneer MRT<br /><strong>Salary</strong>: $3,200 - $3,500<br /></p><p>EA License No.: 96C4864 (Shanice Lim Xin Ni)<br />Reg. No.: R22110485</p>",
